They also don't return the correct items when picked in creative mode.
Factorization barrel, craftpacket stamper and craftpacket maker do something weird with metadata and return incorrect names.
IC2 MVT, HVT, compress, extractor, macerator and glass fiber return incorrect names.
Induction furnace returns incorrect name.
